Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20

Type "# MCP Hub - The package manager for MCP servers"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "mcphub search filesystem"
Enter
Sleep 4s

Type "mcphub search database --all"
Enter
Sleep 4s

Type "mcphub doctor"
Enter
Sleep 12s

Type "mcphub version"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "# Install: curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ricardo-M-L/mcphub/master/install.sh | sh"
Enter
Sleep 2s
